        <tag-mode>multi</tag-mode>
        <tag-value>Sweriges rikes lag 1734 on the left next to a modern 
                    Swedish lawbook from 2023 on the right. 
                    The the old law book is bound in brown leather that has a smooth texure to it except
                    for the occasional dry patch or rough spot. Debossed on the cover is the text "HANDELS-COLLEGIUM."
                    (Board of Trade).
                    The law book from 2023 is bound in a blue, somewhat rough, fabric. The book shows no visible signs of wear and tear as opposed to the older law book.
                    Printed on the 2023 law book in shiny gold is the lesser coat of arms of Sweden.
                    Taken with iteraiton 3
                    setup.
        </tag-value>
